Component: C++ Code Generation Model

A Transformer-based model for generating C++ code from Russian instructions.

Includes:
- Model architecture (Transformer with Pre-LN, GELU activation)
- Training scripts (Tiny/Small/Medium, LoRA fine-tuning)
- Web server for demonstration
- Test suite and evaluation tools
- Russian and C++ BPE tokenizers